{"tid":1170402,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好再拎777同慈禧比","createTime":"2019-05-25T03:34:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-03T19:01:25.000Z","uid":36134,"like":18,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d3caef9ca6a2a4760e3b56d7bf938ac15cd8f054","tid":1170402,"uid":36134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T03:34:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">簡直係侮辱左慈禧</span></span><br />\n當時社會民智未開<br />\n大部分百姓都係反洋人<br />\n加上資訊唔流通<br />\n慈禧本身學識又低 係一個資訊缺乏既情況下 <br />\n做錯決定 好正常<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但今日香港都算係一個發達社會<br />\n資訊流通性極高 <br />\n而777仍然係漠視民意<br />\n岡顧香港人利益<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n777為禍之能絕對係超越古今中外<br />\n只有刁帝可與之一戰"},{"pid":"b2fe8910b93651af732bb193d1e2ea9825b598f1","tid":1170402,"uid":149844,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T03:36:37.000Z","msg":"屎同屎有分別?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n狗屎同人屎都要分?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a97abc3b0e741222e87fa015421c6a332d292a2","tid":1170402,"uid":36134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b2fe8910b93651af732bb193d1e2ea9825b598f1","tid":1170402,"uid":149844,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T03:36:37.000Z","msg":"屎同屎有分別?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n狗屎同人屎都要分?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T03:40:35.000Z","msg":"當時清廷邊個做都一樣<br />\n而家比689上返台 都唔敢好似777咁得罪全世界<br />\n推香港去死"},{"pid":"7447c28be457b29ebceef216f459b615c5546b1a","tid":1170402,"uid":24160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T19:01:25.000Z","msg":"錯 係百姓憎滿洲韃子入骨<br />\n八國聯軍都有相為證 漢人有幫鬼佬入紫禁城"}]}